Being situated in such a central location you have direct access to all forms of public transport, cafes, restaurants and bars. The tenancy has up to 15 car parks available onsite + more can be obtained in the Secure car park behind the building. 

The Milton Green precinct offers dynamic indoor and outdoor areas alongside exceptional amenity and convenience. Being apart of the Milton Green Precinct you have access to:

-  Premium Grade End of Trip facilities incorporating a café, bike repair, towel and dry cleaning service.
-  The Depot – Milton’s first third space encompassing function room, conference facilities, boardrooms, project spaces and a large outdoor entertaining area.
-  The Link – A space that facilitates work, breakout, dining amenity and bookable areas for events
-  Outdoor workspaces with free WIFI, USB Ports and Power Points
-  Yoga Classes and Group Fitness Sessions 
-  On site childcare
-  Diverse array of food and beverage operators within the Park including Bunker Coffee, Bagel Boys, Crust Pizza, Sushi on Cribb and Milton Market food vans
-  Attractive staff and visitor car parking options
-  Tennis Courts, Barbeque Areas, multiple Coffee shops/Cafes, eateries

This is an extremely rare opportunity to secure an office which your staff will actually enjoy coming to work for. For further information or to arrange an inspection contact your Exclusive Marketing Agents CBRE.
